&lt;p&gt;    Test utilities include the StreamingMultipleProgramsTestBase and StreamingTestEnvironment.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    This moves the ITCases for streaming into &apos;flink-tests&apos; to achieve that.&lt;/p&gt;

